    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Level 12+, Ningyo Clan</p><p>You have developed your voixe into a tool more powerful than any weapon, usesble for both offensive and defense</p><ul><li>Increase your Cha or Con by +1</li><li>Any Creature affected by an <em>Audible</em> Genjutsu you are concentrating on is treated as having 1 Rank of <em>Charmed</em> against you.</li><li>Whenever a creature fails a saving throw against a Genjutsu you cast that doesnt deal damage, they immediately take damage from any ranks of <em>Chilled</em> they have.</li><li>You can expend and roll one use of your Ballad die when you cast an Audible Genjutsu. All Concentrations checks made to maintain concentration on that Jutsu, may add the result to the check.</li></ul>",
